"ThoughtWorks meets Berlin at Werkstatt. Werkstatt is host to working sessions, meetings and workshops focussed around our mission to better humanity through software and help drive the creation of a socially and economically just world.

Werkstatt is housed in a quiet courtyard, in an ivy-covered building with scalloped ceiling that recalls its past life as a warehouse. At Werkstatt, communities and groups discover shared concerns, and work together towards common goals."
